371
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:41,770
It's the patient's choice.

372
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:44,010
Yes.

373
00:15:44,480 --> 00:15:45,730
Medicine is difficult,

374
00:15:46,390 --> 00:15:47,460
